.rule_4_5_1_ensure_rip_authentication_is_set_to_md5

Reference: National Security Agency (NSA)

Remediation: If you have deployed RIP in your network you should use MD5 authentication for all
neighbors. To configure authentication enter the following command from the [edit
protocols rip] hierarchy:
[edit protocols rip]
user@host#set authentication-type md5
user@host#set authentication-key <key>

.